---
title: Lebanese-Style Tilapia & Turmeric Rice with Lemony Roasted Carrots & Onion, Hazelnuts
description: This Middle Eastern-style dish was inspired by sayadieh, a rice dish with roots in Lebanon and Syria. It starts with a bed of fluffy golden rice cooked with earthy turmeric and flavorful seafood stock. You’ll serve seared spiced tilapia fillets over the rice along with a colorful jumble of lemony roasted carrots and red onion. Finish this beautiful plate with a shower of crunchy hazelnuts and a sprinkle of fresh parsley for a homestyle meal that may just become your new favorite.
